## Summary

I think writing summaries for science fiction books makes not much sense, but the whole Foundation Series is simply awesome. 7 books in total, they are all worth it. And all the rest of Asimov is worth it too.

Foundation Novels in Order:

- [Foundation](https://amzn.to/3BjRzsl)
- [Foundation and Empire](https://amzn.to/3TQvtoi)
- [Second Foundation](https://amzn.to/3D45NyQ)
- [Foundation's Edge](https://amzn.to/3BjWjy3)
- [Foundation and Earth](https://amzn.to/3RGdnUq)


Prequels: 

- [Prelude to Foundation](https://amzn.to/3KPNIXb) 
- [Forward the Foundation](https://amzn.to/3epBwAa)